      <title>Astera 首次公开募股 7.13 亿美元后，人工智能需求飙升 67%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/astera-soars-46-after-713-million-ipo-snapped-up-on-ai-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者纷纷买入人工智能相关股票，半导体连接公司 Astera Labs Inc. 及其投资者在大规模首次公开募股中筹集了 7.13 亿美元，其股价在首个交易日上涨了 67%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/astera-soars-46-after-713-million-ipo-snapped-up-on-ai-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储推动新兴市场货币连续七个交易日上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/emerging-market-currencies-extend-losses-before-fed-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储坚持今年三次降息的预测后，新兴市场货币扭转了早前的跌势，并在七个交易日中首次上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/emerging-market-currencies-extend-losses-before-fed-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 10:10:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储决定后股市上涨，鲍威尔成为焦点：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储维持 2024 年三次降息的预期，股市上涨，国债收益率下跌，交易员现在将目光转向杰罗姆·鲍威尔的言论，以获取有关央行下一步行动的更多线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 21:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
